      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just the news though. it's the whole point of everything. like, why bother planning a career, or meeting people, or even just trying to stay healthy if the environment is just gonna collapse anyway? it feels like we're all just rearranging deck chairs on the titanic. there’s no actual rhyme or reason to keep going when the end is already written. it just feels like a massive, pointless waste of energy.",
